sources.description:
Creature in the Dark - After strange creatures arrive, a husband waiting for the return of his  wife must take on the role of a father figure to his young daughter. The creatures are attracted to light and it forces them to live in the dark in order to survive.
2020. Stars: Jarrett Ayers, Anthony Derington, Evan Gleason
